.
|-- doc/
|   |-- Files                                   This File
|   |
|   `-- usage_Template.txt                      Template file, Filled in by mkdoc on installation, 
|                                               and during runs of slideshow.pl if the options 
|						file has changed.
|						
|-- .kde/
|   |-- Autostart/
|   |   |-- cron-15min.sh* 			User level cron script.  Runs the slideshow.pl file 
|   |	|					every 15 minutes 
|   |	|					
|   |   `-- cron-1min.sh* 			User level cron script.  Runs the updatecache.pl 
|   |						file every minute.
|   |						
|   `-- share/
|       `-- config/
            |-- glslideshowrc 			Config file for the glslideshow screen saver demo.
|           `-- kdesktoprc 			Config file for the kde screen saver.
|
|-- OpenOffice Macros/
|   |-- ConvertImpresstoPNG.xba 		Macro file for openoffice.  Converts impress files
|   |						to PNG files.
|   |						
|   `-- script.xlb 				Openoffice script registry.
|-- .openoffice.org/
|   `-- 3/
|       `-- user/
|           `-- basic/
|               `-- Standard/
|                   |-- ConvertImpresstoPNG.xba link to OpenOffice Macros/ConvertImpresstoPNG.xba
|                   `-- script.xlb              link to OpenOffice Macros/script.xlb
|-- .openoffice.org2/
|   `-- user/
|       `-- basic/
|           `-- Standard/
|               |-- ConvertImpresstoPNG.xba 	link to OpenOffice Macros/ConvertImpresstoPNG.xba
|               `-- script.xlb 			link to OpenOffice Macros/script.xlb
|-- impress-show.sh*
|-- install.pl* 				install file for the slideshow setup.  Creates all
|						required users/folders and sets correct permissions.
|
|-- mkdoc.pl* 					Builds a quick readme file, based on the values 
|						defined in options.pm.
|
|-- options.pm 					file that stores values used by many of the scripts
|						Must be properly configured for atleast the 
|						workstation name prior to running install.pl
|
|-- slideshow.pl* 				Main processing script.  Checks for magic files and
|						plays them.  Checks for updates/deletes to slideshow
|						documents and runs the conversion.  Runs mkdoc.pl
|						if the options file has changed.
|
|-- updatecache.pl* 				Updates the .xscreensaver-getimage.cache
|
|-- .xscreensaver 				options file for the xscreensaver
|
`-- .xscreensaver-getimage.cache 		cache of all images to display randomly on the 
						screen saver.
